net.proteusframework.ui.search

Class NavigationLinkColumn

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.proteusframework.ui.search.SearchResultColumnImpl
      • net.proteusframework.ui.search.NavigationLinkColumn
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Cloneable, Navigable, SearchResultColumn

    public class NavigationLinkColumn
extends SearchResultColumnImpl
implements Navigable
    Column that includes navigation links for operations such as View, Edit, Copy, and Delete. This uses a FixedValueColumn for its TableColumn by default.

    Delete is accomplished with an action since it is unlikely you want to redirect to another page to delete a record. By default the delete action forwards to the SearchUIOperationHandler,

    Author:
    Russ Tennant (russ@venturetech.net)
